Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.13,0:00:05.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. You've been in Seiran.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.33,0:00:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. I learned that Togetsu\Nhad sent their men to Suoh.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.83,0:00:13.71,Default,,0,0,0,,So I fended them off.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.54,0:00:17.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you fend them off all by yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.08,0:00:21.79,Default,,0,0,0,,That's impossible.\NI had some help from the Seiran soldiers.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.79,0:00:24.38,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, can you brief me about
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.38,0:00:26.92,Default,,0,0,0,,what has happened so far?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.38,0:00:31.50,Default,,0,0,0,,The expansion of the Kunad Gate,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.50,0:00:34.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Togetsu Faith's real motive and their plans.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.88,0:00:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Kagero.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.00,0:00:40.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I never thought you'd be one of the immigrants\Nfrom 2000 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.46,0:00:42.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I look surprisingly young, am I not?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.75,0:00:46.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You people have gathered\Nimportant information.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.58,0:00:48.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Considering what you faced in the secure site,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.29,0:00:49.83,Default,,0,0,0,,you exceeded my expectation.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.83,0:00:50.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.96,0:00:52.71,Default,,0,0,0,,But Naomi...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.71,0:00:53.83,Default,,0,0,0,,And Nagi too...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.42,0:00:58.50,Default,,0,0,0,,We must stop Togetsu's insane ambition.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.00,0:01:02.96,Default,,0,0,0,,But what is Karen planning to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.92,0:01:05.88,Default,,0,0,0,,What we know for certain is that
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.88,0:01:08.42,Default,,0,0,0,,he activated the Red Strings\Nand traveled through time.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.42,0:01:13.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Fubuki, Alice was kept inside Seiran's\NOther research facility, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.83,0:01:19.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. The facility was built so we could\Nturn her back to human.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.42,0:01:22.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew it. That Other was Alice.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.75,0:01:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.63,0:01:26.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Could it be...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.33,0:01:32.50,Default,,0,0,0,,One of the Others that saved us
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.50,0:01:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,was Alice.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.00,0:01:37.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Aunt Alice? But how?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.67,0:01:42.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I think Karen showed up there to save Alice.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.13,0:01:47.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Did I fail again?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.79,0:01:50.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll rewrite it as many times as it takes.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.13,0:01:56.25,Default,,0,0,0,,He traveled back in time\Nto alter Alice's destiny.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.25,0:01:59.21,Default,,0,0,0,,But why was he after Yuito?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.21,0:02:04.50,Default,,0,0,0,,He needed Yuito's power\Nto trigger the Red Strings.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.50,0:02:06.96,Default,,0,0,0,,"As many times as it takes," he said.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.96,0:02:10.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Does it mean it wasn't his first attempt?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.96,0:02:15.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Karen, to think you'd go this far...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.96,0:02:22.38,Default,,0,0,0,,If my memory serves right, Aunt Alice\Nwas your fiancee, Major General Fubuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.38,0:02:23.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.21,0:02:26.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Luka, will you tell the others?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.96,0:02:30.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. Since we'll be working together closely\Nfrom now on,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.54,0:02:33.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to keep any secrets from them.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.13,0:02:39.13,Default,,0,0,0,,For Karen and I,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.13,0:02:42.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Alice was our comrade in the OSF
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.29,0:02:44.25,Default,,0,0,0,,and also our childhood friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.25,0:02:52.29,Default,,0,0,0,,The three of us had known each other\Nfor so long.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.13,0:03:02.67,Default,,0,0,0,,SCARLET NEXUS
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.92,0:03:16.96,Default,,0,0,0,,♫Felling of tiredness is losing yourself♫
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.96,0:03:20.17,Default,,0,0,0,,♫How do you still create a relationship each other♫
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.17,0:03:22.08,Default,,0,0,0,,♫It’s my awkward friend’s fault♫
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.08,0:03:25.42,Default,,0,0,0,,♫Until death, wanting someone somewhere to embrace me♫
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.42,0:03:27.96,Default,,0,0,0,,♫While the devil is not here and between the chaos♫
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.96,0:03:30.29,Default,,0,0,0,,♫Aiming between win and lose♫
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.29,0:03:36.71,Default,,0,0,0,,♫Not to be running out of patience for now\NI’m trying to be careful♫
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.00,0:03:41.42,Default,,0,0,0,,♫You'll see I'm always on your side♫
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.08,0:03:45.71,Default,,0,0,0,,♫I tried hard to connect today as well♫
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.71,0:03:48.17,Default,,0,0,0,,♫You’re frigid and your roller\Ncoaster inside the brain♫
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.17,0:03:51.46,Default,,0,0,0,,♫The grungy days and the unprecedented catastrophy♫
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.63,0:03:55.96,Default,,0,0,0,,♫Where is the glory buried♫
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.96,0:03:58.38,Default,,0,0,0,,♫The lonely monster in a moment♫
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.38,0:04:01.71,Default,,0,0,0,,♫The bullet shot by the machinegun goes parallelly♫
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.71,0:04:04.08,Default,,0,0,0,,♫To pierce with the theory♫
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.13,0:04:09.71,Default,,0,0,0,,♫I tried hard to connect today as well♫
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.21,0:04:14.79,Default,,0,0,0,,♫The bullet shot by the machinegun goes parallelly♫
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.29,0:04:18.79,Default,,0,0,0,,♫It’s the same today\NTo connect vividly♫
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.79,0:04:22.08,Default,,0,0,0,,♫You’re frigid and the theory in the brain♫
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.38,0:04:24.46,Default,,0,0,0,,KAREN'S AMBITION
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.46,0:04:26.58,Default,,0,0,0,,"KAREN'S AMBITION"\NWhen we first met Karen,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.58,0:04:29.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Alice and I were still little kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.96,0:04:32.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Alice, are you really going?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.00,0:04:36.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think you need to rush it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.17,0:04:41.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Maria from our class has already been scouted.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.67,0:04:43.29,Default,,0,0,0,,That's unacceptable.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.21,0:04:49.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Getting scouted early doesn't make one\Nan outstanding OSF soldier.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.42,0:04:51.58,Default,,0,0,0,,But I want to be scouted as soon as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.58,0:04:54.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to become a soldier of OSF\Nto protect everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.63,0:04:58.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll get my check-up done and\Nprove to them I have the power.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.42,0:05:05.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Would the hospital examine you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.92,0:05:08.13,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I need my dad to...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.88,0:05:17.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you all right? Do you need a doctor?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.21,0:05:19.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave me alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.92,0:05:32.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't need anyone's help.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.58,0:05:36.67,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong with him?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.63,0:05:52.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew it. They won't examine you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.83,0:06:02.83,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.92,0:06:17.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Luka, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.00,0:06:25.67,Default,,0,0,0,,The next day, we came to the hospital again
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.67,0:06:27.79,Default,,0,0,0,,because we were worried about Luka.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.63,0:06:38.58,Default,,0,0,0,,The two brothers had been staying\Nin the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.58,0:06:40.63,Default,,0,0,0,,He seemed very rude.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.63,0:06:44.04,Default,,0,0,0,,But it wasn't long before we learned\Nhow kind and gentle he was.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.04,0:06:46.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I am Alice Ichijo.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.17,0:06:48.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I am Fubuki Spring.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.21,0:06:49.75,Default,,0,0,0,,What is your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.88,0:06:52.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Karen.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.13,0:06:53.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Karen Travers.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.50,0:07:00.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, Alice and I started to visit him\Nat the hospital every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.63,0:07:03.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Soon enough, we became friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.13,0:07:05.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You too, Luka.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.42,0:07:08.17,Default,,0,0,0,,But why was he at the hospital?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.17,0:07:10.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Both of them were.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.88,0:07:12.79,Default,,0,0,0,,That was because my brother and I
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.79,0:07:15.13,Default,,0,0,0,,weren't born with any power.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.13,0:07:17.42,Default,,0,0,0,,We were Bell Peppers.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.42,0:07:19.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Bell Peppers?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.25,0:07:23.58,Default,,0,0,0,,The test subject seems to have no recollection\Nof ever being a Bell Pepper.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.63,0:07:27.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Fubuki, did you...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.75,0:07:30.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I know. Karen told me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.79,0:07:32.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.92,0:07:38.33,Default,,0,0,0,,My brother and I were test subjects\Nof a power development experiment.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.25,0:07:44.75,Default,,0,0,0,,They treated us like animals.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.00,0:07:52.54,Default,,0,0,0,,The only hope we had
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.54,0:07:54.79,Default,,0,0,0,,came from Alice and Fubuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.38,0:07:58.25,Default,,0,0,0,,They told us about the world out there,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.25,0:08:02.71,Default,,0,0,0,,their school, families, and friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.71,0:08:05.71,Default,,0,0,0,,For the two little boys who were\Nlocked inside the hospital,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.71,0:08:08.29,Default,,0,0,0,,their stories were brilliant.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.29,0:08:10.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Once we've developed our powers,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.71,0:08:13.75,Default,,0,0,0,,we'd be part of that brilliant world too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.63,0:08:18.38,Default,,0,0,0,,That was the thought that kept us alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.83,0:08:22.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Karen's strength gave Alice and me courage.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.83,0:08:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter what happens, we must never give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.83,0:08:30.08,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong with her?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.08,0:08:33.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Another classmate has been scouted by the OSF.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.88,0:08:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Is my power really so useless?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.21,0:08:52.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Alice's power is matter creation.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.46,0:08:53.79,Default,,0,0,0,,What about yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.08,0:09:01.75,Default,,0,0,0,,This is amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.75,0:09:03.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I am just as determined
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.75,0:09:09.13,Default,,0,0,0,,to join the OSF and help our people\Nas anyone else in the class.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.13,0:09:13.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You are too weak to realize that wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.04,0:09:16.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.13,0:09:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter what it takes,\NI will make it out of this place!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.75,0:09:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right. I can't fall behind either.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.00,0:09:27.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't overdo it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.63,0:09:30.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Karen, keep up the good work\Nso you can get discharged.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.83,0:09:32.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.17,0:09:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Who cares?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.00,0:09:37.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be waiting for you too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.42,0:09:41.96,Default,,0,0,0,,After that, we can always be together.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.96,0:09:47.25,Default,,0,0,0,,What is a fiancee?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.25,0:09:50.33,Default,,0,0,0,,We are getting married when we grow up.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.33,0:09:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Is Alice marrying Fubuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.00,0:09:53.25,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.25,0:09:55.88,Default,,0,0,0,,But it was our family's decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.63,0:10:03.88,Default,,0,0,0,,That sounds great.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.08,0:10:24.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.46,0:10:27.79,Default,,0,0,0,,We detected some minor reactions.\NContinue the attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.79,0:10:28.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.54,0:10:41.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Karen.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.04,0:10:42.38,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll be waiting for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.38,0:10:44.71,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll always be together.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.63,0:11:10.83,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.21,0:11:36.46,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.46,0:11:38.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.13,0:11:43.38,Default,,0,0,0,,He stole his opponent's power!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.50,0:11:55.42,Default,,0,0,0,,After that, my brother was recruited by the OSF.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.21,0:11:59.54,Default,,0,0,0,,At the same time, I was scouted too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.54,0:12:02.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I was in the same cohort as Karen.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.54,0:12:06.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Karen!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.42,0:12:23.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Soon after, Alice joined OSF too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.08,0:12:30.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Alice Ichijo.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.38,0:12:32.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Officially reporting in.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.75,0:12:35.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Congratulation on making it to the force, Alice.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.25,0:12:37.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I finally caught up with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.13,0:12:40.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not going to let you two get\Nall the spotlight.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.04,0:12:44.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't overdo it, newcomer.\NYou might get yourself into trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.13,0:12:48.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard that just not so long ago
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.71,0:12:52.13,Default,,0,0,0,,someone had to write a report as punishment\Nfor disobeying his superior.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.13,0:12:53.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Fubuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.00,0:12:56.67,Default,,0,0,0,,That's worth remembering.\NIt's your 50th report.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.67,0:13:00.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't keep something so funny from her.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.21,0:13:03.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Karen could be one of the next Septentrions,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.71,0:13:06.50,Default,,0,0,0,,but he keeps disobeying orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.50,0:13:09.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't plan to follow any unreasonable orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.79,0:13:13.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You might as well just get a promotion\Nand be a commander yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.92,0:13:16.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to look after the weaklings.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.79,0:13:19.42,Default,,0,0,0,,We should leave that to Fubuki instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.42,0:13:23.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, you care about your comrades.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.33,0:13:27.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, why don't both of you become commanders?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.46,0:13:28.88,Default,,0,0,0,,That could work.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.88,0:13:32.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Karen can be the top commander\Nwhile I work as his aide.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.21,0:13:35.38,Default,,0,0,0,,We could restructure the current army\Ninto different regiments.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.38,0:13:37.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't decide everything yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.63,0:13:57.04,Default,,0,0,0,,We fought the enemy forces together.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.04,0:13:59.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Alice's fighting skills had improved as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.00,0:14:23.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.58,0:14:33.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for saving me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.50,0:14:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't let your guard down.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.88,0:14:37.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.04,0:14:40.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder how many times you've saved me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.83,0:14:42.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You two, are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.17,0:14:44.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Fubuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.75,0:14:47.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad you are safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.04,0:14:50.29,Default,,0,0,0,,This fool got careless again.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.29,0:14:51.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It wasn't anything too serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.75,0:14:54.88,Default,,0,0,0,,And you've become even stronger.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.88,0:14:57.42,Default,,0,0,0,,But make sure you don't get too reckless.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.13,0:14:59.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Karen, you're hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.83,0:15:01.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, it was my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.58,0:15:02.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll treat your wound now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.17,0:15:04.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Never mind. It's just a scratch.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.33,0:15:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Fubuki, Alice is exhausted.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.50,0:15:09.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep her company.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.54,0:15:11.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll check the other areas.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.50,0:15:13.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Karen!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.96,0:15:19.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Two years later...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.88,0:15:23.88,Default,,0,0,0,,The Extinction Belt has reached\Nthe lower altitude of certain areas.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.88,0:15:26.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a rare phenomenon.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.21,0:15:29.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Brain talk will be disabled.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.54,0:15:30.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't let your guard down.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.33,0:15:53.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll take point.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.38,0:15:55.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Karen, don't rush too far ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.88,0:15:58.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I can handle it here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.96,0:16:00.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Alice, assist Karen.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.79,0:16:01.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.04,0:16:35.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Karen!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.08,0:16:46.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Alice!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.83,0:16:48.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Alice!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.38,0:16:59.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Alice!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.50,0:17:06.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Alice...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.33,0:17:20.17,Default,,0,0,0,,What...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.17,0:17:21.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Alice...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.92,0:17:28.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Alice, is that you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.08,0:17:29.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Alice, stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.46,0:18:04.33,Default,,0,0,0,,The same happened to my sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.33,0:18:08.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Alice was sent to the OSF hospital afterward.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.75,0:18:11.38,Default,,0,0,0,,She was treated as a test subject.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.33,0:18:17.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Only the government and a handful of people\Nknow about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.13,0:18:22.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You want to bust Alice out of the hospital?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.38,0:18:27.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you even know what the consequences will be?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.79,0:18:29.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You cannot stop me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.71,0:18:33.25,Default,,0,0,0,,If you refuse to help, I'll do it myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.88,0:18:37.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you found a place to settle her down?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.63,0:18:44.08,Default,,0,0,0,,My family owns Spring Pharmaceuticals.\NThey have a base in Seiran.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.08,0:18:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You could use that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.25,0:18:49.63,Default,,0,0,0,,We got Seiran to assist us
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.63,0:18:53.83,Default,,0,0,0,,and successfully rescued Alice\Nfrom the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.83,0:18:56.79,Default,,0,0,0,,But for a very long time after the rescue,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.79,0:18:59.71,Default,,0,0,0,,the best we could do was imprisoning Alice.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.71,0:19:02.88,Default,,0,0,0,,We saved her,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.88,0:19:06.67,Default,,0,0,0,,but also set her on a worse fate.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.63,0:19:09.17,Default,,0,0,0,,We were so lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.33,0:19:15.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought about giving up.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.71,0:19:19.38,Default,,0,0,0,,But Karen refused to listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.08,0:19:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,He insisted on saving Alice.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.54,0:19:26.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, we can always be together.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.92,0:19:31.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Karen traveled back in time
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.04,0:19:34.33,Default,,0,0,0,,to change Alice's fate.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.33,0:19:36.29,Default,,0,0,0,,That seems to be the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.29,0:19:39.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Karen did travel through time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.42,0:19:42.33,Default,,0,0,0,,But Alice didn't come back to life.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.33,0:19:46.96,Default,,0,0,0,,He went back in time,\Nbut nothing has changed in the present.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.96,0:19:49.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Did he run into some setbacks?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.71,0:19:51.00,Default,,0,0,0,,We wouldn't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.00,0:19:54.58,Default,,0,0,0,,But we can focus on what we can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.58,0:19:55.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I agree.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.96,0:19:57.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.13,0:19:59.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Karen's intention still worries me,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.25,0:20:02.38,Default,,0,0,0,,but the more pressing matter\Nis to stop Togetsu's plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.38,0:20:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,But how?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.00,0:20:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,,We can stop Togetsu's mainframe,\NBABE, from functioning.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.50,0:20:09.42,Default,,0,0,0,,How does that sound?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.42,0:20:11.38,Default,,0,0,0,,The researches on Red Strings
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.38,0:20:15.92,Default,,0,0,0,,and their plans of operations are all in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.92,0:20:17.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Under these circumstances,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.83,0:20:21.13,Default,,0,0,0,,if you came up with the most viable plan,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.13,0:20:23.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll follow your lead.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.42,0:20:25.88,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're stopping Togetsu's plan,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.88,0:20:27.83,Default,,0,0,0,,is there anything I can do to help?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.83,0:20:31.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you deal with Suoh and Seiran?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.42,0:20:33.83,Default,,0,0,0,,If the tension between them ease up,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.83,0:20:36.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Togetsu's operation will be undermined.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.67,0:20:39.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll try my best to make them\Ncall for a truce.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.96,0:20:44.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Both Suoh and Seiran have\Nvery little trust in Togetsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.04,0:20:47.83,Default,,0,0,0,,That should be enough to persuade both sides.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.83,0:20:49.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll try my best.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.04,0:20:51.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't overdo it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.92,0:20:54.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll leave the rest to you, Sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.71,0:20:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,That means we must infiltrate Togetsu's base.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.00,0:20:58.79,Default,,0,0,0,,How can we get in there?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.79,0:21:02.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Based on the information Kagero and Kyoka have,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.13,0:21:04.63,Default,,0,0,0,,we could come up with a plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.63,0:21:07.33,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll need your help, Kagero, Kyoka.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.33,0:21:09.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.42,0:21:12.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Kagero?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.21,0:21:24.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I think we can still use that cavern system.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.75,0:21:27.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the same passage we used to escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.63,0:21:30.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Are we going to run into that Other again?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.21,0:21:33.08,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think, Kagero?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.75,0:21:39.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, but can we discuss the plan later?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.67,0:21:45.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuito, before we set out for Togetsu,\NI need to have a word with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.08,0:21:46.54,Default,,0,0,0,,A word with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.54,0:21:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's not talk about it here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.00,0:21:50.29,Default,,0,0,0,,We should talk outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.29,0:21:53.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Since everyone is present,\Nyou should listen to it too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.38,0:21:59.13,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this about?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.96,0:22:02.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It's your father.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.92,0:22:06.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It's about Chairman Sumeragi.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.25,0:22:07.58,Default,,0,0,0,,My father?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.83,0:22:10.96,Default,,0,0,0,,The man who killed him
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.83,0:22:13.08,Default,,0,0,0,,was me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.00,0:22:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,♫I'm troubled by my own yearning♫
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.50,0:22:45.42,Default,,0,0,0,,♫Unveil the blocked sun ray♫
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.42,0:22:47.50,Default,,0,0,0,,♫There's a stranger in me♫
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.50,0:22:50.04,Default,,0,0,0,,♫That I've never seen♫
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.04,0:22:54.96,Default,,0,0,0,,♫I can not soar in the sky without fear♫
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.96,0:22:57.13,Default,,0,0,0,,♫I'm spreading my wings♫
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.13,0:22:59.46,Default,,0,0,0,,♫Dancing gracefully like a bird♫
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.46,0:23:04.08,Default,,0,0,0,,♫And gazing towards the scarlet sky♫
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.08,0:23:09.42,Default,,0,0,0,,♫I chased after the gust♫
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.42,0:23:14.67,Default,,0,0,0,,♫The scenery spreads into\Nthe ever-changing world♫
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.67,0:23:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,♫Inside the intertwined brilliance♫
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.00,0:23:24.21,Default,,0,0,0,,♫I'm still searching for tomorrow's direction♫
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.04,0:23:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,♫Tomorrow's in your hands♫
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.50,0:23:28.54,Default,,0,0,0,,♫Don't tell me now you're afraid♫
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.79,0:23:31.29,Default,,0,0,0,,♫There's no time to waste♫
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.29,0:23:33.33,Default,,0,0,0,,♫Go forward♫
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.46,0:23:38.79,Default,,0,0,0,,♫Have no fear for anything♫
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.79,0:23:40.25,Default,,0,0,0,,♫Now, let's go♫
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.25,0:23:45.42,Default,,0,0,0,,♫Into a brand new day♫
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.67,0:24:05.92,Default,,0,0,0,,KAGERO'S CONFESSION
